data.description: LARGE BRICK FRONT COLONIAL ON 1/3+ ACRE!  This is an ESTATE SALE. Available for immediate sale.  Property in being sold AS-IS.  Property has 4 spacious bedrooms including an owner’s suite with walk-in closets, soaking tub, his and her vanity, 3 full and 1 half bathrooms, hardwood and carpet flooring, library/office on main level, living room, separate dining room, kitchen with island and table space, large family room with vaulted ceiling, fireplace and sliding doors, laundry on main level, spacious two car garage and 4 car parking in driveway, large basement with walk-up. Great location with access to Andrews AFB, DC and VA.   Property needs updating, cosmetic repairs and the deck needs significant repairs or replacement. GREAT OPPORTUNITY to transform this property into your dream home!
